will not MQ the Chardok and KC pipes, and I will not in any way MQ my epic.  MQing/buying the components are signs of sure weakness.  For you Iksar Monks, take the punishment for being a hated race, work on faction, do the headband quests yourself you lazy pieces o' crap!  I have said what I wanted, flame away.<br><br>Gesthal Vecter - Current 44 Monk of Xegony.<br>(Wow, that was long ;)</p>&nbsp;<br>To all you Non-Monks, you can't FD when 7 Wizzies are chain-casting on you.&nbsp;&nbsp;FD explained. =)</td></td></tr>
